QuestData.Title: Return to the Surface
QuestData.Description: You should leave now. You'll find a portal behind me. It'll take you to the surface.$B$BWe'll meet again. He'll be looking for you.$B$BIt's only a matter of time until he finds you.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return to Thassarian aboard the Skybreaker.
QuestData.RewardText: It's you, $n! We thought you were a goner.$B$BThat explosion of yours put quite a bit of hurt on the Scourge. Nearly took Captain's Kendall's eyebrows off in the process...
